## 10. Current Validation Rules
- Food listings must use approved active menu items from that mess.
- Waste logs must use a valid active menu item from that mess.
- Student feedback must be associated with a mess.
- Mess and NGO registration block submission when a location cannot be geocoded.
- BioLoop registration also blocks submission when a location cannot be geocoded.

